to all those lawyers.

02:45.479 --> 02:47.683
- It was remarkable.
- Thank you.

02:47.720 --> 02:50.197
Our son Daniel is remarkable, too.

02:51.923 --> 02:54.565
He has been locked up for 25 years.

02:55.095 --> 02:56.918
They said he raped and murdered a girl.

02:56.979 --> 02:58.267
SOPHIA: He's innocent,

02:58.344 --> 03:00.171
and he's got the DNA to prove it.

03:01.982 --> 03:04.439
After my court-appointed lawyer
screwed up my case,

03:04.524 --> 03:07.487
I, uh, spent about five years
feeling sorry for myself.

03:07.610 --> 03:10.298
And then decided, hell,
I'll just do it on my own.

03:10.618 --> 03:13.402
So I got my bachelor's degree,

03:13.439 --> 03:15.173
read everything
about the law that I could.

03:15.238 --> 03:16.649
Even took the LSATs.

03:16.759 --> 03:18.164
Sounds familiar.

03:18.564 --> 03:19.924
MADELINE: You were
convicted of the rape

03:19.960 --> 03:21.368
and murder of Janet Dale.

03:21.432 --> 03:23.189
It's not true. None of it.

03:23.806 --> 03:25.003
I never even met her.

03:25.040 --> 03:27.696
But you were found in the same
bedroom as her dead body.

03:28.259 --> 03:30.087
At the Phi Kappa Delta fraternity.

03:30.407 --> 03:32.205
So, tell us what happened that night.

03:32.242 --> 03:35.272
This guy I knew, Eddie DuBar,
he invited me.

03:35.655 --> 03:36.928
I was still in high school.

03:37.047 --> 03:38.556
Me and my buddies, we, um...

03:38.617 --> 03:40.277
we got into all the frat parties
'cause...

03:40.859 --> 03:42.273
well, we had the best weed.

03:42.389 --> 03:44.072
Look, I'm not gonna lie. I...

03:44.109 --> 03:45.593
I got totally wasted.

03:45.976 --> 03:47.455
Passed out behind some bed.

03:47.492 --> 03:49.286
The next morning, the cops wake me up,

03:49.835 --> 03:52.788
and there's Janet's body, half-naked.

03:52.851 --> 03:54.458
And the police arrested you right away?

03:55.082 --> 03:56.328
Right on the spot.

03:56.421 --> 03:57.628
But I swear

03:57.963 --> 03:59.704
I didn't rape or murder anyone.

03:59.812 --> 04:02.710
I knew I had to test the DNA
they found inside Janet Dale.

04:02.992 --> 04:04.544
There's no way that that matches me.

04:04.912 --> 04:06.124
And I was right.

04:06.459 --> 04:08.576
So the rape kit doesn't match your DNA?

04:08.661 --> 04:10.078
Not even close.

04:10.839 --> 04:13.657
That should be enough
to turn over my conviction?

04:14.132 --> 04:15.688
No rape, no murder.

04:15.725 --> 04:17.209
It's as solid a case as we've seen.

04:17.247 --> 04:18.656
Yeah, you did great.

04:18.838 --> 04:20.683
Now you have
two wrongful conviction lawyers

04:20.720 --> 04:22.386
to help take it over the finish line.

04:23.732 --> 04:25.715
♪ ♪

04:41.663 --> 04:45.046
There are about a million ways
to wind up in prison

04:45.405 --> 04:47.270
but only four ways to get out.

04:47.522 --> 04:49.454
You serve your sentence,
you get paroled,

04:49.491 --> 04:52.374
you leave in a body bag,
or... our personal favorite...

04:52.646 --> 04:54.018
you get exonerated.

04:54.233 --> 04:55.686
For the wrongfully convicted,

04:55.706 --> 04:57.354
a good lawyer is a necessity,

04:57.374 --> 04:59.615
and it can make
all the difference in the world.

05:00.022 --> 05:02.080
But, represented or not,

05:02.149 --> 05:05.104
a prisoner's last resort... is hope.

05:05.959 --> 05:09.377
Hope... that there's a way out.

05:12.515 --> 05:13.747
This is amazing.

05:14.000 --> 05:15.572
From now on, let's only take cases

05:15.609 --> 05:17.329
where the client's already done
all the work for us.

05:17.366 --> 05:18.726
And what would you do
with your free time?

05:18.762 --> 05:19.625
Learn to knit.

05:19.674 --> 05:20.838
EASY: Now, Daniel's conviction

05:20.875 --> 05:22.723
was based solely
on circumstantial evidence.

05:22.836 --> 05:25.119
Right. No injuries consistent
with a struggle

05:25.156 --> 05:27.226
and no eyewitnesses
to the rape or murder.

05:27.295 --> 05:29.726
And the best part? We drew
an ace with our assignment.

05:29.864 --> 05:31.740
Judge Elijah Fry
will hear our petition.

05:31.858 --> 05:33.419
- Nice.
- What am I missing?

05:33.456 --> 05:35.468
EASY: Elijah Fry is the greatest
legal mind of our era.

05:35.543 --> 05:36.919
The Cardozo of Chicago.

05:36.972 --> 05:40.148
He also happens to be
Easy's mentor, teacher,

05:40.209 --> 05:41.875
guide, and inspiration,

05:41.912 --> 05:42.972
all rolled into one.

05:43.009 --> 05:44.877
The man made me the lawyer I am today.

05:44.980 --> 05:47.213
He taught me that truth,
justice and honesty

05:47.250 --> 05:48.734
are more important than anything else.

05:48.822 --> 05:50.080
Cool. So we got an in.

05:50.117 --> 05:51.789
Guys, we have a problem.

05:51.944 --> 05:53.705
Amina, what's going on? Is Davon okay?

05:53.805 --> 05:55.281
He's back on death row.

05:55.349 --> 05:57.211
I was in Madison when I heard.

05:57.328 --> 05:58.508
I drove here straightaway.

05:58.545 --> 05:59.745
I don't understand. What happened?

05:59.781 --> 06:01.072
AMINA: The State of Ohio is saying

06:01.109 --> 06:02.596
that any death row inmate

06:02.633 --> 06:04.497
without an actual
pending appeal will be

06:04.534 --> 06:06.053
put to death as soon as possible.

06:06.249 --> 06:07.442
Why?

06:07.516 --> 06:09.525
Ohio's death drugs are about to expire.

06:09.600 --> 06:11.417
So instead of delaying
the death penalties,

06:11.454 --> 06:13.015
they're speeding up the ones they can.

06:13.066 --> 06:15.603
They are rushing the executions
so they can use

06:15.640 --> 06:17.406
the drugs they do have
before they expire.

06:17.443 --> 06:19.302
Same thing happened in
Arkansas a few years ago.

06:19.339 --> 06:20.414
AMINA: In Ohio,

06:20.451 --> 06:22.875
16 of 127 men on death row

06:22.912 --> 06:26.035
have had their execution dates
moved up. Davon's one of them.

06:26.248 --> 06:28.445
Davon is different. He has a stay.

06:28.507 --> 06:31.547
The Ohio Court of Appeals
vacated Davon's stay,

06:31.584 --> 06:33.117
in support of the legislature.

06:33.178 --> 06:34.724
We're gonna fight this.

06:35.080 --> 06:36.896
Will you excuse us?

06:38.334 --> 06:40.033
- I have to go to Ohio.
- Look, I know.

06:40.115 --> 06:42.218
I'll take the Daniel Hernandez
case. Shouldn't take long.

06:42.466 --> 06:44.041
- I'll see you right after.
- Yeah.

06:44.131 --> 06:45.743
<i>JUDGE FRY:
Good to see you, Mr. Boudreau.</i>

06:45.780 --> 06:47.105
Always a pleasure, Your Honor.

06:47.142 --> 06:50.162
Counsel, Mr. Boudreau was
a student of mine in law school.

06:50.240 --> 06:51.865
That was many years ago.

06:51.934 --> 06:53.801
I assume the State has no objection.

06:53.882 --> 06:55.045
Of course not, Judge.

06:55.082 --> 06:57.351
I also gather,
from petitioner's papers,

06:57.388 --> 07:01.849
there's a serious problem with
Mr., uh, Mr. Hernandez's DNA.

07:01.958 --> 07:03.256
The DNA from the semen

07:03.293 --> 07:05.194
recovered from the
victim's body is not his.

07:05.285 --> 07:06.835
I thought this was a murder case.

07:06.953 --> 07:08.061
It is, Your Honor.

07:08.125 --> 07:09.646
Murder, with an associated rape charge.

07:09.701 --> 07:11.211
Your Honor, the State requests 90 days

07:11.248 --> 07:12.312
to perform its own tests.

07:12.349 --> 07:13.967
No. I don't see any need
for further tests.

07:14.010 --> 07:15.724
I'm prepared to rule now.

07:15.819 --> 07:18.920
Petitioner's DNA being the sole
evidence in the State's case

07:18.957 --> 07:21.492
in support of the rape charge,
this court grants

07:21.529 --> 07:24.302
petitioner's motion to dismiss
count one of the indictment

07:24.339 --> 07:26.852
and vacates said rape conviction.

07:30.857 --> 07:32.781
Counsel, was there something else?

07:32.818 --> 07:34.045
The murder conviction, Judge.

07:34.082 --> 07:36.680
Oh, yes, of course.
Well, the murder charge stands.

07:36.741 --> 07:38.231
[GALLERY MURMURING]

07:38.990 --> 07:41.762
All due respect, Judge,
the two charges are inseparable.

07:41.930 --> 07:43.422
My client didn't rape Ms. Dale,

07:43.459 --> 07:44.947
he also didn't murder her.

07:45.041 --> 07:46.443
Can't have one without the other.

07:46.543 --> 07:47.834
FRY: Of course you can.

07:47.936 --> 07:49.867
