07:49.904 --> 07:52.529
Your Honor, Illinois case law
clearly holds the opposite:

07:52.716 --> 07:56.468
"The inextricability of rape and
murder counts almost inevitably

07:56.505 --> 07:58.466
requires the dismissal of both."

07:58.611 --> 08:01.052
The key word being "almost."

08:01.162 --> 08:04.642
That's enough, Ezekiel,
you have my ruling.

08:08.279 --> 08:10.778
I've never heard of separating
two charges out like that.

08:11.138 --> 08:13.068
So what now? We file an appeal?

08:13.105 --> 08:15.315
Judge Fry is brilliant and respected.

08:15.480 --> 08:18.484
